{"tid":1376360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"理性分析  法律撚請入","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T05:35:16.000Z","uid":56274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78d3f40cf607ee2f432e950ea63e398bfe2feac7","tid":1376360,"uid":56274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"關於凌駕性<br />\n<br />\n香港憲法 （基本法）<br />\n法律<br />\n條例<br />\n守則<br />\n<br />\n層層下遞之下<br />\n基本法《第二十七條 》<br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家佢唔批準預先申請既遊行<br />\n<br />\n但依家香港市民每人自發遊行 佢有咩權力去阻止<br />\n當佢阻止我地所做既野 係唔係違左憲"},{"pid":"6dcbc6c9e0eb8c4680af755881e4bfa330cd2f3a","tid":1376360,"uid":56274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"推一推 問一問"},{"pid":"21ca583848a2c8f473a69340234e5feb9976d342","tid":1376360,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"係梁國雄案終院判詞講過公安條例就示威遊行所施加既限制係合憲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/panels/se/papers/se1101cb2-192-5c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr05-06%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse1101cb2-192-5c.pdf&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=93147d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/panels/se/papers/se1101cb2-192-5c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"3491b26b5335fae6ffe80c3b4245fb4e51f3107b","tid":1376360,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ca583848a2c8f473a69340234e5feb9976d342","tid":1376360,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"係梁國雄案終院判詞講過公安條例就示威遊行所施加既限制係合憲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/panels/se/papers/se1101cb2-192-5c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr05-06%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse1101cb2-192-5c.pdf&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=93147d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/panels/se/papers/se1101cb2-192-5c.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n好似唔係咁解<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄案係由於完全無事前通知處長judgement話事前通知處長係合憲,所以梁被合理定罪。<br />\n<br />\n而有關處長可否施加限制，同梁國雄案無關，所以冇作任何judgement。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即係無討論到不反對通知書是否合憲。</span>"},{"pid":"ddf3274de68fa3a8015ba4d2a52d5afed4f194aa","tid":1376360,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"香港有法律既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54d02d87e6c7f54e377f8d828692dc48a311341","tid":1376360,"uid":56274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3491b26b5335fae6ffe80c3b4245fb4e51f3107b","tid":1376360,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ca583848a2c8f473a69340234e5feb9976d342","tid":1376360,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"係梁國雄案終院判詞講過公安條例就示威遊行所施加既限制係合憲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/panels/se/papers/se1101cb2-192-5c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr05-06%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fpapers%2Fse1101cb2-192-5c.pdf&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=93147d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/panels/se/papers/se1101cb2-192-5c.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n好似唔係咁解<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄案係由於完全無事前通知處長judgement話事前通知處長係合憲,所以梁被合理定罪。<br />\n<br />\n而有關處長可否施加限制，同梁國雄案無關，所以冇作任何judgement。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即係無討論到不反對通知書是否合憲。</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"終於有人明我既意思......<br />\n唔知可唔可以係呢度入手"},{"pid":"fa4affd237f6caa7d0d282a9f5ab75e4df525279","tid":1376360,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e54d02d87e6c7f54e377f8d828692dc48a311341","tid":1376360,"uid":56274,"like